  "description": "<p>Welcome to Two Men Bagel House.</p>\n<p>WE are looking to hire!</p>\n<p>Looking for a suitable candidates for this role.</p>\n<p>- Head chef/Manager Trainee.</p>\n<p>Job descriptions include:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>organization of inventory</li>\n  <li>lead costings and pricing strategies</li>\n  <li>managment of operations</li>\n  <li>lead research and development in menu creation</li>\n  <li>conduct ops manning/ rostering</li>\n  <li>build team morale together with assistant directors with building key goals and plans for the restaurant</li>\n  <li>Career pathway to be a manager of 1 or more outlets.</li>\n  <li>Possible overseas posting or exchange.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
